        7
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Borough_(New_Jersey)"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The 1897 Borough Act removed the ability for towns to incorporate on their own, requiring legislative approval for new boroughs.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        14
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Borough_(New_Jersey)"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Alpha sits in Warren County, just 4 miles west of Phillipsburg and about 70 miles west of New York City, near the Delaware River border.",
